ckaging/Training/Logs/2009-08-13\">Colin Watson kindly reviewed my changes</a>.</li>\n<li>I attached a new diff.gz to the <a href=\"https://bugs.launchpad.net/ubuntu/+source/ldtp/+bug/412882\">bug report</a> with the changes Colin had suggested.</li>\n<li>I went for lunch. By the time I came back the new LDTP package had been sponsored and uploaded to universe. Again, just in time before holidays and Karmic feature freeze.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Teamwork rocks!</p>\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gocomments/ubuntutesting.wordpress.com/105/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/comments/ubuntutesting.wordpress.com/105/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/godelicious/ubuntutesting.wordpress.com/105/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/delicious/ubuntutesting.wordpress.com/105/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gostumble/ubuntutesting.wordpress.com/105/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/stumble/ubuntutesting.wordpress.com/105/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/godigg/ubuntutesting.wordpress.com/105/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/digg/ubuntutesting.wordpress.com/105/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/goreddit/ubuntutesting.wordpress.com/105/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/reddit/ubuntutesting.wordpress.com/105/\" /></a> <img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://stats.wordpress.com/b.gif?host=ubuntutesting.wordpress.com&amp;blog=4261311&amp;post=105&amp;subd=ubuntutesting&amp;ref=&amp;feed=1\" /></div>" "http://ubuntutesting.wordpress.com/2009/08/13/perfect-timing/" (19076 9738) old 16 nil nil ((title nil "Ara Pulido: Perfect timing") (guid nil "http://ubuntutesting.wordpress.com/?p=105") (link nil "http://ubuntutesting.wordpress.com/2009/08/13/perfect-timing/") (desc